examples.text: fındık shottır hayata keyif katan...Herzaman diil tabii. Bazen...

examples.translation: The houses are drunk, not me ;)

examples.text: öğleden önce Arnavutköyden ( boğaz diil) Tuzlaya denetime gidicem, patron artık bi uçak alsın yazık bana
examples.translation: Before noon I'm going from Arnavutköy (not the Bosphorus) to Tuzla for inspection, [my] boss should buy me a plane, woe is me.
